These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-4-1::.
House: palace, cottage, ranch-style, gothic-revival
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, tulip, daffodil, orchid
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, february, january, december
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, golf, parkour, sailing
There are 4 different favourite colors: ebony, coral, azure, ivory
 1. the palace house is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person who likes azure is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 3. the person who likes ivory is on the left of the person who likes coral##1
 4. the person who growsdaffodil is in an odd position##4
 5. the person who growsorchid is the person who growsorchid##1
 6. the person who likes azure is on the far right##1
 7. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in december##3
 8. the person who likes ebony is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
 9. the ranch-style house is on the left or right of the person who growstulip##3
10. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left or right of the person who growsdaffodil##3
11. the palace house is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
12. the person who's birthday is in january is between the person who growsdaffodil and the person who's birthday is in february##2
13. the ranch-style house is the person who likes ivory##1
14. the person who likes azure is the cottage house##1
15. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the cottage house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3      |     4      |
| House           | palace | ranch-style | gothic-revival  | cottage    |
| Flower   | tulip     | orchid   | daffodil  | balloon-flower  |
| Birthday           | february        | january    | december        | august |
| Sport         | sailing    | golf      | biathlon   | parkour    |
| Color     | ebony  | ivory     | coral | azure |

