.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-4-2::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: pink, apricot, mauve, green
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, camping, magic-tricks, singing
The people have 4 different jobs:  manager, accountant, analyst, pilot
4 different pets are kept: turtle, guinea-pig, goat, hamster
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, january, december, august
 1. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the accountant##1
 2. the person who likes apricot is on the right of the accountant##1
 3. the person who likes pink is in an odd position##4
 4. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 5. the pilot is the person who's birthday is in january##1
 6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far left##1
 7. the person who likes green is in an even position##4
 8. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is camping##3
 9. the pilot is on the left or right of the person who likes green##3
10. the person who's hobby is board-games is the person who's birthday is in august##1
11. the person who likes mauve is on the far left##1
12. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the manager##1
13. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2       |    3    |      4      |
| Color      | mauve        | green       | pink    | apricot       |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks | camping      | singing | board-games |
| Job   | pilot     | analyst | accountant  | manager   |
| Pet   | guinea-pig   | hamster         | turtle   | goat      |
| Birthday         | january      | november     | december    | august      |

