.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-4-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola, lemonade, fanta
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: sports, satire, musical, epic
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, house, indie, jazz
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, fonseca, aristoff, bolivar
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, nigerian, italian, polish
 1. the fonseca-smoker is the fan of house##1
 2. the fan of house is on the left of the canadian##1
 3. the polish is in an odd position##4
 4. the chaman-smoker is on the left or right of the person watching sports movies##3
 5. the italian is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
 6. the fonseca-smoker is on the left or right of the aristoff-smoker##3
 7. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3
 8. the canadian is on the right of the polish##1
 9. the fonseca-smoker is in an odd position##4
10. the person drinking lemonade is the fan of indie##1
11. the fan of jazz is on the left of the fonseca-smoker##1
12. the fan of jazz is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
13. the aristoff-smoker is the person drinking fanta##1
14. the fan of indie is on the left of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3     |     4     |
| Beverage          | lemonade | cola | coffee     | fanta |
| Movie-Genre           | musical  | epic   | sports | satire  |
| Music-Genre   | indie  | jazz      | house     | country   |
| Cigar         | bolivar | chaman  | fonseca   | aristoff    |
| Nationality     | italian | nigerian    | polish     | canadian |

