.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-4-4::.
City: marseilles, paris, rome, liverpool
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, basketball, volleyball, baseball
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, fanta, juice, cola
House: craftsman, gothic-revival, tower, art-deco
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, quad-bike, snowmobile, tram
 1. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the art-deco house##1
 2. the person drinking juice is the person traveling to rome##1
 3. the person traveling to paris is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
 4. the person drinking cola is between the person driving the jet-ski and the person driving the snowmobile##2
 5. the craftsman house is on the far left##1
 6. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
 7. the tower house is on the left or right of the craftsman house##3
 8. the gothic-revival house is the person driving the quad-bike##1
 9. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
10. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
11. the person who's sport is baseball is in an odd position##4
12. the person traveling to marseilles is the person who's sport is baseball##1
13. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left or right of the person traveling to paris##3
14. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##3
15. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |      3      |        4        |
| City         | liverpool | paris    | marseilles | rome       |
| Sport           | basketball | lacrosse  | baseball   | volleyball |
| Beverage   | iced-tea   | fanta     | cola      | juice            |
| House           | craftsman       | tower      | gothic-revival    | art-deco           |
| Transport     | tram      | snowmobile | quad-bike   | jet-ski         |

