The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, d&b, blues, dubstep
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, australian, polish, argentine
There are 4 different favourite colors: ebony, brown, ivory, fuchsia
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, handball, skateboarding, volleyball
 1. the person who's sport is volleyball is between the person who's sport is skateboarding and the person playing canasta##2
 2. the fan of blues is in an even position##4
 3. the australian is on the right of the fan of blues##1
 4. the fan of dubstep is in an even position##4
 5. the person who likes brown is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
 6. the person who likes fuchsia is on the right of the australian##1
 7. the person playing go is on the left or right of the person who likes brown##3
 8. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left or right of the person who likes brown##3
 9. the fan of jazz is the person playing snooker##1
10. the person playing canasta is the argentine##1
11. the fan of jazz is the chinese##1
12. the person who likes ivory is the australian##1
13. the person who likes brown is in an even position##4
14. the person playing canasta is the fan of dubstep##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2       |      3      |       4        |
| Game          | snooker   | scrabble        | go      | canasta      |
| Music-Genre           | jazz | blues         | d&b   | dubstep |
| Nationality   | chinese       | polish          | australian | argentine        |
| Color           | ebony         | brown    | ivory    | fuchsia         |
| Sport         | handball     | skateboarding | volleyball  | cycling        |

