 4. the polish is in an odd position##4
 5. the person watching family movies is the person traveling to marseilles##1
 6. the mexican is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
 7. the person watching time-travel movies is the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 8. the pakistani is the person playing monopoly##1
 9. the person traveling to berlin is on the far left or far right##3
10. the colonial house is the person playing go##1
11. the person watching time-travel movies is in an odd position##4
12. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
13. the gothic-revival house is in an odd position##4
14. the pakistani is between the colonial house and the person traveling to berlin##2

