 7. the person who's hobby is dancing is the person who likes blue##1
 8. the person who's hobby is hiking is between the person who's birthday is in january and the person who likes aquamarine##2
 9. the person who growsamaryllis is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an even position##4
