.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-4-8::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, trance, folk, country
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, jet-ski, bus, train
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, snooker, whist, canasta
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, drama, horror, western
House: modern, futuristic, cape-cod, palace
 1. the fan of trance is in an odd position##4
 2. the person playing whist is the palace house##1
 3. the futuristic house is the person watching drama movies##1
 4. the modern house is the fan of folk##1
 5. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
 6. the fan of trance is between the futuristic house and the person playing whist##2
 7. the fan of country is between the person watching horror movies and the person watching western movies##2
 8. the person playing canasta is on the right of the modern house##1
 9. the person driving the train is on the left or right of the person watching comedy movies##3
10. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the fan of country##1
11. the person driving the jet-ski is the person playing whist##1
12. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |      3       |    4     |
| Music-Genre      | folk    | country      | trance      | rock |
| Transport          | ship | bus | train       | jet-ski |
| Game         | mah-jongg   | canasta   | snooker | whist  |
| Movie-Genre   | horror    | drama    | western      | comedy   |
| House         | modern   | futuristic     | cape-cod       | palace  |

