There 4 different types of food: lemon, broccoli, cherry, pumpkin
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, roller, skateboard, subway
 1. the person who likes aquamarine is between the person watching martial-arts movies and the person eating pumpkin##2
 2. the person who likes brown is in an even position##4
 3. the person who likes azure is the person eating lemon##1
 4. the person eating lemon is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
